{"tid":536353,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇諗過情人節送咩比另一半","createTime":"2018-01-21T16:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T03:46:46.000Z","uid":92511,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"25cac5ae2bafe280f613fefec644f4bbca2c4531","tid":536353,"uid":92511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:44:52.000Z","msg":"黎緊情人節就係同男朋友一齊既第二個情人節<br />\n呢一段時間同佢經歷左好多野 上年整左朱古力比佢 今年送咩好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我依家諗過係情侶衫？整銀包比佢？<br />\n巴絲們有冇諗過 就黎到喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce70d1a85953bf60510afe6135176625217aec0b","tid":536353,"uid":78349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:45:58.000Z","msg":"Lm先<br />\n手做銀包生日送左 而家唔知送乜好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28fd15f4660442b81c5df5bbc1701834ad4d143d","tid":536353,"uid":71524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:47:20.000Z","msg":"煮餐飯俾佢食<br />\n次次都係佢煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似搞到我唔識煮咁"},{"pid":"62a03e947071198c4b4f10a15dea836c8b7da6b2","tid":536353,"uid":89134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:50:57.000Z","msg":"送個處比男朋友"},{"pid":"6424ae1512a80de5248544a66e04d897b6346ea0","tid":536353,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:57:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e03c1fec58f1790663d2d59638907f538dbd8e0","tid":536353,"uid":162959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T23:38:00.000Z","msg":"今年你都可以整野食俾男友架，例如蛋糕，一餐飯，曲奇之類<br />\n<br />\nbtw 我同男友今年情人節都唔買禮物俾對方 因為想儲錢去旅行"},{"pid":"2884c6037206250c0348e949d795fca5ad824202","tid":536353,"uid":149357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-22T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"第一個情人節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj